.SH NAME
_base_wait_for_doorbell_int \- waiting for controller interrupt(generated by a write to the doorbell)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" _base_wait_for_doorbell_int
.BI "(struct MPT3SAS_ADAPTER *ioc "  ","
.BI "int timeout "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ioc" 12
per adapter object
.IP "timeout" 12
timeout in seconds
.SH "RETURN"
0 for success, non-zero for failure.
.SH "NOTES"
MPI2_HIS_IOC2SYS_DB_STATUS - set to one when IOC writes to doorbell.
